 nice to support automatic conversion of old scripts to new scripts. Not sure if this is feasible.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<h1 id=\"markdown-header-summary\">Summary</h1>\n<p>Models that contain &lt;material&gt;&lt;script&gt; tags currently do not work with Ogre1, and may never work with ogre2.  For example see <a href=\"https://app.ignitionrobotics.org/openrobotics/fuel/models/Textured%20Shapes\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://app.ignitionrobotics.org/openrobotics/fuel/models/Textured%20Shapes</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"markdown-header-motivation\">Motivation</h1>\n<p>It would be nice to support automatic conversion of old scripts to new scripts. Not sure if this is feasible.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2019-01-28T21:59:40.282114+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2019-01-28T21:59:40.282114+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 10}